## Ruling the country is boring... the King wants to go on an adventure!

The Adventurous King is a strategic puzzle adventure game. Hire adventurers at the campsite, find loot and fight monsters!

This is my 2nd attempt at Ludum Dare and my first jam ever using Godot. The graphics are hand drawn and digitally coloured. You can't vote for audio because I've added it after the jam's deadline. Controller is supported! Check the change log below for all post jam bug fixes and improvements.

This game is inspired by Pikmin, Overlord and Little King's Story. Royalty free music by [Always Music](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO6a3ndAxXkoJwz-ubtbyIQ) and [Royalty Free Zone](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCehIXMLpmRqDzqB5Ov89v5A).

