Here is a little clicker/roguelike where you have to find your own parts of the body.

Gameplay:
1. Enter the zone;
2. Character will automatically move around trying to find what he needs;
3. Gain experience and level-up your character (increase ```defense```, ```max hp``` and ```skill points per level multiplicator```);
4. Move to next zone and repeat until you find the final part of character (guess what).

